text: Adeesha Thilanchana (born 23 June 1995) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Sri Lanka Army Sports Club in the 2014–15 Premier Trophy on 16 January 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Sinhalese Sports Club cricketers Category:Sri Lanka Army Sports Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
